column5: Hey guys, I just booked a trip to Sand lake through Air Cochrane and was wondering if anyone whent there how was the fishing ?  Thanks
Not sure, but have a great trip!   Looks like an interesting little lake to fish.  Here's a [cleaner] depth map for you: http://www.lineonfishing.com/images/Ontario_Outpost_Lake_Maps/Sand.pdf
Should be good I seen on another forum a guy caught 800 walleye in 4 days with two guys but that was In 2009 but it should be good fishing
